    "body": "## Summary\r\n- SM120 devices (RTX 5080/5090) lack thread block cluster support\r\n- Force `cluster_n=1` in `_set_cluster_n()` for RMSNorm forward and backward\r\n- Existing `const_expr(self.cluster_n > 1)` guards compile away all cluster code automatically\r\n- Softmax and CrossEntropy to follow in subsequent commits\r\n\r\n## Test plan\r\n- [x] `test_rmsnorm_forward_backward` — passed (N=192, N=4096)\r\n- [x] `test_rmsnorm_with_residual` — passed\r\n- [ ] `test_softmax` — pending\r\n- [ ] `test_cross_entropy` — pending\r\n- [ ] Full test suite on SM120\r\n\r\nTested on RTX 5080 (SM120, compute capability 12.0).",
    "created_at": "2026-04-04T19:34:08Z",
